name: S
caption: Fixed ordering/setup cost
message: The fixed ordering/setup cost must be positive.

name: h
caption: Unit holding cost per unit of time
message: The unit holding cost per unit of time must be positive.

name: A
caption: Mean of the demand per unit of time
message: The mean of the demand per unit of time must be positive.

name: b
caption: Std. Dev. of the demand per unit of time
message: The standard deviation of the demand per unit of time must be positive.

name: AL
caption: Mean of the Lead-time
message: The mean of the lead time must be positive.

name: bL
caption: Std. dev. of the Lead-time
message: The standard deviation of the lead time must be nonnegative

name: CSL
caption: Cycle service level
message: The cycle service level must be in the interval(0, 1).

name: FR
caption: Fill rate
message: The fill rate must be in the interval (0, 1).
